## Model Licenses

### Custom ML Models
The pre-trained ML models used in this project (`PiGrieco/mcp-memory-auto-trigger-model`) 
are licensed under the MIT License and are freely available for use, modification, 
and distribution.

### Base Models
This project may use base models from HuggingFace Hub. Please refer to the specific 
model cards for their individual licenses:
- Most models are under Apache 2.0 or MIT licenses
- Some models may have specific usage restrictions
- Commercial use permissions vary by model

